-- Bundesbank says critical of ECB collateral decision
-- 
-- Fri Jun 22, 2012 9:48am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/06/22/us-ecb-collateral-bundesbank-idUSBRE85L0R320120622

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Germany's Bundesbank voiced its concern on Friday over a European Central Bank decision to start accepting a wider range of collateral in its lending operations as well as assets of a lower quality. 
 "The Bundesbank is critical (of the move)," a spokesman said. (Reporting by Andreas Framke, writing by Paul Carrel)